隻m2起啲boot/efi partition同裝bootloader令佢bootable <br />\n<br />\n以下你當廢話睇<br />\n你夠technical可以揾其他live usb, resize windows parition起返三兩個啱flag嘅partition出黎 再入windows 隻usb 行啲command 起返partition同copy boot files/ install bootloader  有堆installtion specific id/partition id 之類要打啱command先fix到個installation 開得返 <br />\n我整過一次 係會boot到 但唔係原生之後開唔到bitlocker"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T15:38:48.000Z","msg":"好啦, 當汲取教訓。<br />\n本來諗住砌哂ssd/hhd入去, 一次過唔使煩，點知會有呢d問題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}